]},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"loading","type":"text"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If button is placed on colored surface using ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSColoredSurface","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the default colors (content, background and border) are automatically adjusted to switch to monochrom.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A button with ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSButton.Appearance.Negative","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" appearance is not allowed as a direct or indirect child of an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSColoredSurface","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Icon only with default appearance","    OUDSButton(icon: Image(\"ic_heart\"), accessibilityLabel: \"Like\", appearance: .default) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","","    \/\/ Text only with negative appearance","    OUDSButton(text: \"Delete\", appearance: .negative) {}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For accessibility reasons, if the user in the system settings toggles the option to reduce the animations, the loading indicator will be frozen to be more comfortable for the user."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For ecodesign reasons, if the user toggles the low power mode, the loading indicator will be frozen to prevent the CPU to work and waste energy."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/actions"]}],"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"metadata":{"images":[{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","type":"card"}],"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"title":"Actions"},"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"